There comes this kind of tipping point where it stops being simply individual transformation and you start to see it showing up in the structures of society.

39:24.662 --> 39:33.672
Certain industries start closing shop because there's no more demand for those industries anymore because so many hearts have been changed.

39:33.692 --> 39:37.596
It's not that they go and they root out those industries by the power of politics.

39:37.936 --> 39:40.439
There's nobody who wants the stuff anymore.

39:40.459 --> 39:42.962
That's how radical the change is.

39:43.330 --> 39:45.412
begins to be felt in the culture.

39:45.432 --> 39:47.595
That's what happened in Kidderminster England, the 1600s.

39:47.655 --> 39:50.618
Richard Baxter comes there and it's an utterly pagan town.

39:50.959 --> 40:00.930
Nobody worships Jesus when he leaves practically everyone on every street in Kidderminster is worshiping God, exalting Christ.

40:00.950 --> 40:04.254
You imagine if God began saving that way in Birmingham?

40:07.057 --> 40:08.178
If there was that kind of

40:08.546 --> 40:11.230
Faith, meaningful, genuine conversion.

40:11.250 --> 40:12.953
I'm not talking about the watered down.

40:13.013 --> 40:15.977
God is my co-pilot faith that is so prevalent in our city.

40:16.698 --> 40:19.622
I'm talking about radical transformation.

40:21.325 --> 40:24.109
Hearts completely new, changed by Jesus Christ.

40:24.129 --> 40:29.397
Talking about burn piles, if you will, all over this city filled with stuff that our culture calls God.

40:32.582 --> 40:34.885
That's revival.

40:34.905 --> 40:35.506
Pray for that.

40:36.834 --> 40:39.640
pray for that in our city, pray for that in our world.

40:39.680 --> 40:40.642
God loves to do that.

40:40.682 --> 40:41.203
Verse 20.

40:42.205 --> 40:44.490
So the word, here's his summary, Luke's summary.

40:45.372 --> 40:49.761
So the word of the Lord continued to increase and prevail mightily.

40:49.801 --> 40:55.574
The word, I love this phrase because it actually runs through, weaves through critical turning points throughout the book of Acts.

40:55.995 --> 40:57.618
The word is personified.

40:57.858 --> 40:59.301
throughout the book of Acts.

40:59.341 --> 41:07.019
Matter of fact, one commentator even went so far as to say, the word might be considered the chief character in the narrative of Acts as a whole.

41:08.262 --> 41:09.906
The word is doing the work.

41:11.522 --> 41:16.908
Acts 6 verse 7 and the word of God continued to increase and the number of the disciples multiplied greatly in Jerusalem.

41:17.008 --> 41:17.689
Acts 12, 24.

41:18.150 --> 41:19.671
The word of God increased and multiplied.

41:19.771 --> 41:20.552
Acts 13, 49.

41:20.953 --> 41:23.075
And the word of the Lord was spreading throughout the whole region.

41:23.356 --> 41:24.176
Acts 19, 20.

41:24.277 --> 41:27.781
So the word of the Lord continued to increase and prevail mightily.

41:27.841 --> 41:32.466
The word, the word, the word is just transforming everywhere it goes.

41:32.746 --> 41:34.068
It's rocking people.

41:34.128 --> 41:36.050
It's rocking cultures.

41:36.930 --> 41:39.813
Awesome, turning the world upside down.

41:39.833 --> 41:47.560
In a profound way, I think that we could hang Isaiah 55, 11 over the whole of the book of Acts as an explanation of everything you see here.

41:49.702 --> 41:53.066
So shall my word that goes out from my mouth.

41:54.027 --> 42:02.735
It shall not return to me empty, but it shall accomplish that which I purpose and shall succeed in the thing for which I sent it.

42:04.137 --> 42:05.618
That's what we see in the book of Acts.

42:05.762 --> 42:07.825
God's word is not coming back empty.

42:07.865 --> 42:14.353
No matter where it goes, it's coming back with its hands full of sinners saved by the power of grace.

42:15.114 --> 42:16.035
It's an awesome thing.

42:17.818 --> 42:25.047
This almost wrote, some may trust in horses, some trust in chariots, but we will trust in the name of the Lord our God.

42:26.389 --> 42:33.618
We trust church in the spirit who works through the proclamation of the gospel and this gospel

42:33.858 --> 42:34.640
renovates.

42:35.141 --> 42:38.829
This gospel runs quickly throughout the earth.

42:38.869 --> 42:40.653
This gospel overpowers evil.

42:42.217 --> 42:49.874
Now prayer is that this gospel would bring revival, revival to the city, revival to the world so that there is

42:49.954 --> 42:51.577
inside the culture of Birmingham.

42:51.637 --> 42:53.640
There is a culture within the culture.

42:53.660 --> 43:08.824
There's a counterculture, kingdom culture in the city of Birmingham showing the rest of Birmingham, outside of Christ Birmingham, what it looks like to be under the lordship of Jesus Christ and his kingdom of righteousness, peace, and joy.

43:08.904 --> 43:09.805
That's our desire.

43:09.865 --> 43:11.167
That's our hope.

43:11.188 --> 43:15.314
We won't stop until we see God doing that work in the world, amen?

